---
const note = `When my own business was growing, I realised I was spending more time on admin than on the work that actually moved the needle. The more tools I added, the more things broke silently. I wanted one thing — an operations system I could trust without constantly checking on it.

That is how PURIST started.

We assembled an engineering team of automation architects and AI specialists we genuinely respect, gave them a single instruction — answer to the ROI, not the hype cycle — and built the workflows from there. Every automation had to earn its place. Anything we could not prove saved time or money got cut.

What you get is an operations backbone. Not a silver bullet, not a shortcut. The reliable foundation that lets the rest of your business work better.

Thank you for trusting us with that.`;
---

<section class="bg-brand-cream py-20 lg:py-28">
  <div class="container-x grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
    <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-4">A note from our founder</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-h1 mb-8 text-balance">
        Built for businesses <em class="font-medium">that refuse to waste time.</em>
      </h2>
      <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none text-base lg:text-lg text-brand-gray-900/80 leading-relaxed">
        {note.split('\n\n').map((para) => <p>{para}</p>)}
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <p class="font-display text-xl italic">[Founder Name]</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-brand-gray-600">Founder, PURIST</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
      <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-image overflow-hidden bg-brand-sand">
        <img
          src="/images/founder/portrait.svg"
          alt="PURIST founder"
          width="480"
          height="600"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
